{"tid":635202,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"終於 都到我。","createTime":"2018-04-20T02:51:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T05:19:59.000Z","uid":86127,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"248adeb6cb5685022530a3f2a120a2abc910ac1f","tid":635202,"uid":86127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"我以為自己係你眼中真係有所不同<br />\n以為自己真係你既小天使<br />\n但原來所有野都係好短暫 來去快過龍捲風<br />\n我既優點你唔會再留意到 更加唔會再欣賞我<br />\n諗起以前你想tum我開心 一杯雪糕就會令我笑翻<br />\n所有既點滴 你都唔會再做 <br />\n到底要點接受所有開心既回憶都已經過去？<br />\n<br />\n大半個月黎每日剩係食到一餐<br />\n呢幾日直情食唔落野 訓唔到教<br />\n係唔係被人拋棄都會咁<br />\n我好想企翻起身<br />\n好想好好愛錫自己 自私d<br />\n但係我做唔到 最後都因為怕煩到你而唔搵你<br />\n從你既世界消失 我知道你既世界無左我<br />\n你就會開開心心<br />\n<br />\n到底失戀第一步係點 <br />\n有無條formula 比我跟等我快啲好翻？"},{"pid":"70dd2472fc4f3b327b3fd1e88ba325ab99273885","tid":635202,"uid":182362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:00:02.000Z","msg":"快啲搵返個咪得囉 呢到大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca729f51071b3b9c72f8d76888282a09d48d600","tid":635202,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:04:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com&d=jxAsTADpIS2eYGc%2BVBnRAEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=a25f5ba0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com</a>"},{"pid":"88269e75f3e08ffdbabe4a023afd32ed76230502","tid":635202,"uid":1546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:11:00.000Z","msg":"算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd6359b2066f316911d76d21b928784bb941904d","tid":635202,"uid":144843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T03:26:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"807587469ef73d5a090a390983da0e251125e6d2","tid":635202,"uid":86127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>快啲搵返個咪得囉 呢到大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔係想要仔呀<br />\n我想要開開心心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e17b465eb6c86f3e0c4536a4d1a0945f8a60d821","tid":635202,"uid":21355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T04:56:15.000Z","msg":"做其他嘢分散下注意"},{"pid":"7393d0c0e97dbecc5bbbdde30bfc3573cc3d008b","tid":635202,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:02:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1b8bf06859bbb2df52c83d9d40c4c1a0c7e047cb","tid":635202,"uid":62920,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"開心咪得囉，如果唔開心嘅又何苦互相折磨呢？<br />\n唔開心一排完再重要起返身，依段日子只能靠自己。無人幫到你，都唔好搵人幫，到頭黎只怕故事一直重覆。"},{"pid":"93865155f6da4c95250bc069f6186c8a8fc9bccf","tid":635202,"uid":155038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"抽身啦清"},{"pid":"1ce0e58f0d931f2f38cefd3bf2936fdd003b0a93","tid":635202,"uid":182567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"認真同唔認真都係咁答<br />\n我見親人地失戀, 一有新仔就老豆姓乜都唔記得晒, 之前講到幾慘都係廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516471ecc3cea65b7cb19ed4676d82d4cc356a47","tid":635202,"uid":174488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T09:34:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bd53dcb6eeb44c9e8822db760020654c13f6f0ff","tid":635202,"uid":93395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T09:49:13.000Z","msg":"搵過個distract下啦<br />\n<br />\n最有效架啦 自己一個on99有排都唔好"},{"pid":"453265a5e6d506548bf828617a0da68a70a8a7c9","tid":635202,"uid":86127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:19:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開心咪得囉，如果唔開心嘅又何苦互相折磨呢？<br />\n唔開心一排完再重要起返身，依段日子只能靠自己。無人幫到你，都唔好搵人幫，到頭黎只怕故事一直重覆。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得開心 無論佢脾氣幾臭 我都覺得係佢身邊好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我無搵人幫 迫自己狂讀書計數<br />\n都係好掛住佢 食唔落野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}